All orders of Alcon lenses, including Total1, Precision1, and Dailies Aqua Comfort Plus will experience long delays from 19th Dec until 9th Jan.

Hi Lee,
We apologise that all Alcon lens orders, including all Total1, Precision1 and Dailies Aqua Comfort Plus from Monday Dec 19th until Sunday Jan 8th will be delayed. We ship direct from Alcon to typically give the fastest delivery times. Alcon are changing warehouses during this period, so there is blackout, with delay, on all Alcon orders received during this period. We apologise for the inconvenience.

If you need more Alcon lenses, please order before midnight on Sunday December 19th to avoid delays. Just click one of the blue buttons below to order now.
